<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>中汇招标登录页面</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/base.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/footer.css">
		<style>
			body {

				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.login_top {
				width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.login_logo {
				text-align: left;
				width: 300px;
				height: 80px;
				padding: 20px 0px;
				/* background: #008FED; */
				color: #ffffff;
			}

			.login_content {
				width: 100%;
				background: url(../img/login_bg.jpg) center center no-repeat;
				height: 600px;
			}

			.login_center {
				width: 1200px;
				margin: 0 auto;

			}

			.login_login {
				margin-top: 20px;
				width: 320px;
				height: 430px;
				float: right;
				border-radius: 3px;
				background: #ffffff;
				z-index: 999;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.login_login h2 {
				text-align: center;
				color: #008FED;
				height: 100px;
				line-height:100px;
				font-size: 28px;
				
			}
			.login_login form p {
				margin-top: 5px;
				color: red;
			}
			.user_number {
				width: 94%;
				height: 40px;
				line-height: 40px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				background: #e6e6e6;
				padding:0px 10px;
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #3C3C3C;
				border: none;
			}
			.user_psd {
					width:94%;
				height: 40px;
				line-height: 40px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				background: #e6e6e6;
				padding:0px 10px;
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #3C3C3C;
				margin-top: 20px;
				border:none;
				
			}
			.login_btn {
				
				margin-top: 30px;
					width:100%;
				height: 40px;
				line-height: 40px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				background: #008fed;
				padding:0px 10px;
				font-size: 14px;
				color: #ffffff;
				border:none;
				cursor: pointer;
				
			}
			.check {
				width: 100%;
				height: 50px;
				line-height: 50px;
				vertical-align: middle;
				
			}
			.check span {
				height: 50px;
				line-height: 50px;
				
			}
			.check input {
				color:#646464;
				height: 50px;
			vertical-align: middle;
				margin-right: 6px;
				
			}
			.fr {
				color:#646464;
				float: right;
			}
			.reg {
				margin-top: 50px;
				height: 50px;
				line-height: 50px;
				text-align: left;
				font-size: 16px;
         }
			.reg a {
			color: #008FED;
				}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="login_top">
			<div class="login_logo">
				<img src="../img/logo.png" alt="">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="login_content">
			<div class="login_center">
				<div class="login_login">
					<h2 style="font-size: 20px;">用户登录</h2>
					<form action="#" method="post">
						<input class="user_number" type="text" placeholder="请输入账号" name="login" />
						<p style="display:none;">账号不正确</p>
						<input class="user_psd" type="password" placeholder="请输入密码" name="psd" />
						<p style="display:none;">密码不正确</p>
						<div class="check">
							<input class="fl" type="checkbox" /><span>记住密码</span>
							<span class="fr"><a href="#">忘记密码？</a></span>
						</div>
						<input class="login_btn" type="button" value="登录" />
					</form>
					<div class="reg"><a href="registe.html">新用户注册</a></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="footer_content">
				<div class="footer_info">
					<ul>
						<li><a href="#">关于我们</a>|<a href="#">联系我们</a>|<a href="#">免责声明</a>|<a href="#">隐私政策</a>|<a href="#">友情链接</a>|<a
							 href="#">法律声明</a>|<a href="#">广告服务</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<p class="footer_p"> 版权所有 北京中汇恒升互联网有限公司 Powered by LingJiang tech 京ICP备18005946号-7</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
